      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SEMI PEAKIN' (1) recorded a Grade 4/5 win two back then missed the frame last time at this track, but drawn Box 1 this time where he has won before. Looks suited here and big improvement expected. RED AURA (2) finds it hard to break through. Finished in the minors latest when second (22.53) at Gosford and may be close to breaking through. Form here sound including three wins. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from four attempts. Expecting another good run. NO SHARES (8) scored two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 8 length 6th at Gosford (22.74). The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Great chance to atone. LISA'S VOGUE (7) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
